lay: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;\"><span>Loft/Lie förändring</span> <strong>50 kr</strong></li>\n        <li style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;\"><span>Förlängning <small>(inkl. plugg)</small></span> <strong>150 kr</strong></li>\n        <li style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;\"><span>Kapning</span> <strong>50 kr</strong></li>\n        <li style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;\"><span>Omlimning lösa huvud</span> <strong>150 kr</strong></li>\n        <li style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 8px 0;\"><span>Spikbyte skor <small>(exkl. spik)</small></span> <strong>150 kr</strong></li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"price-category\" style=\"background: #f9f9f9; padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #eee; grid-column: 1 / -1;\">\n      <h3 style=\"border-bottom: 2px solid #000; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0;\">Skaft & Komponenter</h3>\n      <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 20px;\">\n        <ul style=\"list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;\">\n          <li style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;\"><span>Skaftbyte <small>(arbete)</small></span> <strong>300 kr</strong></li>\n          <li style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;\"><span>Sleevebyte <small>(arbete)</small></span> <strong>150 kr</strong></li>\n          <li style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;\"><span>Adapter Driver/Fairway</span> <strong>350 kr</strong></li>\n          <li style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 8px 0;\"><spa